kubectl config get-contexts
kubectl config view

apiVersion: v1

# 集群配置
clusters:
- cluster:
    certificate-authority-data: 
    server: https://127.0.0.1:6443
  name: kubernetes-1
- cluster:
    certificate-authority-data: 
    server: https://127.0.0.1:6443
  name: kubernetes-2

# 用户配置
users:
- name: kubernetes-admin-1
  user:
    client-certificate-data: 
    client-key-data: 
- name: kubernetes-admin-2
  user:
    client-certificate-data: 
    client-key-data: 
# 上下文配置
contexts:
- context:
    cluster: kubernetes-1
    user: kubernetes-admin-1
  name: kubernetes-admin-1@kubernetes-1
- context:
    cluster: kubernetes-2
    user: kubernetes-admin-2
  name: kubernetes-admin-2@kubernetes-2
current-context: kubernetes-admin-1@kubernetes-1
kind: Config
preferences: {}

## ETCD检查
etcdctl --ca-file=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/ca.crt --cert-file=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.crt --key-file=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.key --endpoints https://127.0.0.1:2379 cluster-health
